\c 48
\s Jakove anoropafadza vanakomana vaJosefa
\p
\v 1 Shure kwaizvozvo Josefa akaudzwa, zvichinzi, Tarira, baba vako vanorwara; iye akatora vanakomana vake vaviri, Manase naEfuremu.
\v 2 Jakove akaudzwa, zvichinzi, Tarirai, mwanakomana wenyu, Josefa, wauya kwamuri. Israeri akazvisimbaradza, akagara pauvato.
\v 3 Zvino Jakove akati kuna Josefa, Mwari Wemasimbaose akazviratidza paRuzi, panyika yeKenani, akandiropafadza,
\v 4 akati kwandiri, Tarira, ndichakuberekesa, ndichakuwanza, ndichakuita ndudzi zhinji; ndichapa vana vako vanokutevera nyika ino, ive yavo nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 5 Zvino vanakomana vako vaviri, vawakaberekerwa panyika yeEgipita, ndisati ndasvika kwauri paEgipita, ndavangu; Efuremu naManase vachava vangu savana Rubheni naSimioni.
\v 6 Asi vana vako, vawakabereka shure kwavo, vachava vana vako, vachatumidzwa nezita ravakuru vavo panhaka yavo.
\v 7 Kana ndirini, pakubva kwangu paPadhani, ndakafirwa naRakeri panyika yeKenani munzira ndasvika pedo neEfurata, ndikamuvigapo panzira inoenda Efurata (rimwe zita ndiBheterehemu).
\p
\v 8 Israeri akaona vanakomana vaJosefa, akati, ndivana aniko?
\p
\v 9 Josefa akati kuna baba vake, Ndivo vanakomana vangu vandakapiwa pano naMwari. Vakati, Douya navo kwandiri ndivaropafadze.
\v 10 Zvino meso aIsraeri akange oona madzerere nokukwegura, akange asisagoni kuona. Akavaswededza kwavari, Israeri akavatsvoda, akavambundikira.
\v 11 Israeri akati kuna Josefa, Handina kufunga kuti ndichaona chiso chakozve, zvino tarira, Mwari akandionesa navana vakowo.
\v 12 Josefa akavabvisa pakati pamabvi avo akakotamira pasi nechiso chake.
\p
\v 13 Josefa akavabata vari vaviri, Efuremu norudyi rwake kuruboshwe rwaIsiraeri, naManase noruboshwe rwake kurudyi rwaIsraeri, akavaswededza pedo naye.
\v 14 lsiraeri akatambanudza ruoko rwake rworudyi, akaruisa pamusoro paEfuremu, aiva muduku, noruoko rwake rworuboshwe pamusoro waManase, akapesanisa maoko ake achizviziva, nekuti Manase aiva wedangwe.
\p
\v 15 Akaropafadza Josefa, akati, Mwari uya, akafamba madzibaba angu pamberi pake, vana Abhurahamu naIsaka, Mwari akandifudza paupenyu hwangu hwose kusvikira zuva ranhasi;
\v 16 mutumwa wakandidzikunura pane zvakaipa zvose, ngaaropafadze vanakomana ava; zita rangu ngaritumidzwe kwavari, namazita amadzibaba angu, Abhurahamu naIsaka, vawande kwazvo panyika.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Josefa akati achiona kuti baba vake vaisa ruoko rwavo rworudyi pamusoro waEfuremu, hazvina kumufadza, akabata ruoko rwababa vake, kuti arubvise pamusoro waEfuremu, aruise pamusoro waManase.
\v 18 Josefa akati kuna baba vake, Regai kudaro, baba vangu, nekuti ndiye wedangwe, isai ruoko rwenyu pamusoro wake.
\p
\v 19 Baba vake vakaramba, vakati, Ndinoziva, mwana wangu, ndinoziva; naiyewo achava rudzi, naiye achava mukuruwo, asi munin'ina wake achava mukuru kwaari, vana vake vachava ndudzi zhinji.
\p
\v 20 Akavaropafadza nomusi iwoyo, akati, Newe vaIsraeri vacharopafadza, vachiti, Mwari ngaakuite saEfuremu naManase. Akaisa Efuremu pamberi paManase.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Israeri akati kuna Josefa, Tarira, ndofa, asi Mwari achava nemi, achakudzoserai kunyika yamadzibaba enyu.
\v 22 Newe ndinokupa mugove mumwe kupfuura vamwe vana vababa vako, uya wandakatorera vaAmori nomunondo wangu nouta hwangu.
